Random Thoughtsw

Why Sweet Dreams?

Goodnight, sweetdreams!

Think about it, when you have a sweetdream you wake up disappointed after that alarm hits right in your face and brings you back to reality. Now lets say you had the worst nightmare then when you wake up you feel relieved that it was just a dream. I'd personally prefer the 2nd one.

Want to read another Book like 'Kiss Before Dying' before dying

There are two kinds of authors - ones who go on and on about the color of the sky, surroundings, dresses, appearences etc., and the other kind who prefer to spend time inside a characters head meddling with good and bad. The latter, my fav kind and this book my fav from that kind (yeah, he spent far too much time on copper mining in the end chapters but I think its justified in this case (shows us where truly Bud's heart lied all this time, dude never felt a single thing about any of the 3 sisters.)
